<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida92c7602-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s2125"><num value="2125">§ 2125.</num><heading> Members of the program: exclusion from authorized strengths</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Notwithstanding any other provision of law, members of the program shall not be counted against any prescribed military strengths.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ida92c7603-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/92/426/s2/a">Pub. L. 92–426, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="1972-09-21">Sept. 21, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/718">86 Stat. 718</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
